{"tid":1711400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高主教書院學生受打壓  請求大家協助","createTime":"2019-11-12T11:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:32:26.000Z","uid":33586,"like":69,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"052fbd66735f6ba7adb24c29f95bf203a0e32473","tid":1711400,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"見到隔離有個post話 德望學校扮中立打壓學生<br />\n其實高主教書院亦面對同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校指希望冷處理 但實際上打壓學生自由 討好建制陣營的校友<br />\n<br />\n校友陣容鼎盛如下：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張建宗<br />\n曾偉雄<br />\n鄭承隆<br />\n鄭耀棠<br />\n石禮謙<br />\n<br />\n舊生會更加由成日話要打曱甴比人起埋底嘅快＿美太子爺把持<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆被迫改名為意見牆</span></span></strong><br />\n校方指連儂牆帶有政治意味以及較近示威者的立場，因此理應保持中立，易名為意見牆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5／11早會默站行動及Lunchtime操場靜坐</span></span></strong><br />\n早前有校內學生被補，校內關注組發起早會默站行動以聲援被捕同學。<br />\n校方以活動期參加者有機會提及被捕同學，對其保釋有所影響而禁止。<br />\n校方以律師之名施壓指校內的一切聲援活動會引發同學討論，而只要談及便足以影響案件。<br />\n而靜坐行動，校方則指有同學需要打籃球，生怕靜坐同學被球打中而趕走他們連最和平的聲音也不能接受<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有舊生返校聲援師弟妹 被拒進校門</span></span></strong><br />\n最後導致堅道荼記被圍一事<br />\n因上報傳媒，校方立刻派人補獲<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">副校L. Yeung 指學校內不談政治，而又指並無打壓言論自由</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><strong>緊急關頭不停課 不理學生死活</strong></strong></strong></span></span><br />\n學校位於半山區，不少同學放學走路至中環搭車<br />\n中環多次放催淚彈，放學時分更形同戒嚴<br />\n有不少同學遭共軍恐嚇截查<br />\n有舊生打去問高層，高層指學校唔係直資，所以教育局唔停課就無得停<br />\n因為停咗會比教育局cut資源<br />\n學生性命比學校資源更低賤<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>學校如何確保學生翻學放學安全？</strong></span></span><br />\n校方指而家無學生有事，無收到投訴，所以暫時好安全<br />\n有同學表示11號在學校聞到催淚煙<br />\n但校方無收到學生因為聞到煙味而不適<br />\n並表示如果真係有，學校有措施可以比佢早走<br />\n學生覺得唔舒服可以唔返，不過要有家長信同家長通知<br />\n<br />\n學生在校中無地位，之前全靠舊生施壓才成功取得少少成果<br />\n而家更關乎自身安全問題，希望各位手足幫手推，通知傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n施加輿論壓力先可以令學校關注學生的訴求"},{"pid":"01c81bb525b16126c2f464203dccb2ec5b3f3edf","tid":1711400,"uid":158438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fb1746d5c0ea61c5359633847a5d59bd6c0d8aa5","tid":1711400,"uid":219120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:31:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6718876be2806ddc50ba5827d49ee29bdb0e8f9","tid":1711400,"uid":34045,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"我哋好難幫到手，好多地方都可能有事發生，你哋唔團結屌個副校之後都係會俾佢打壓/秋後算賬"},{"pid":"5e1dd905aec5716c72a6d8b5ae64e59b0326f5c7","tid":1711400,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/CmyrFgR.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"d9783faa07106cde4dd9f478cdaa924bd53a9262","tid":1711400,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ff8197489b7ad70d6aae3e9cccbd19b759f98ce","tid":1711400,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6718876be2806ddc50ba5827d49ee29bdb0e8f9","tid":1711400,"uid":34045,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"我哋好難幫到手，好多地方都可能有事發生，你哋唔團結屌個副校之後都係會俾佢打壓/秋後算賬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:38:34.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家繼續關注暴大"},{"pid":"6a112a9f29f48e2f5cf65ebb88bd1f7a723d8630","tid":1711400,"uid":136700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"1fd3360a489346f0a1f724631d29253b4976053c","tid":1711400,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3169933f2d0723ae9027d4b200f994bf023387a9","tid":1711400,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"ob一推 要求停課"},{"pid":"0600ef96b91d698c69f8d1cb5268b05c4050c2ca","tid":1711400,"uid":190579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"L Yeung<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2affbafb9594403bb362514135ed3c02ddfa3b3f","tid":1711400,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:07:27.000Z","msg":"多謝各位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n校內無計可施 先會出post<br />\n得閒推下就得 外面開花更加重要"},{"pid":"7e132b872a915b22c5ba0256297799893286618b","tid":1711400,"uid":1124,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"高記仔頂住<br />\n利申： 舊生"},{"pid":"733e6f0a8f8b9910e6c93752993d649bfd8509f0","tid":1711400,"uid":52859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"48d36723fa55a9f1cba5011b3047a0e94c79d0d8","tid":1711400,"uid":119546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11f8620dc315b0e3a988f1fdccc0563ef0cd27cd","tid":17114