\n並表示如果真係有，學校有措施可以比佢早走<br />\n學生覺得唔舒服可以唔返，不過要有家長信同家長通知<br />\n<br />\n學生在校中無地位，之前全靠舊生施壓才成功取得少少成果<br />\n而家更關乎自身安全問題，希望各位手足幫手推，通知傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n施加輿論壓力先可以令學校關注學生的訴求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:16:24.000Z","msg":"利用校董會"},{"pid":"6327f8af930e96998af1a27804c328ef98de9742","tid":1711400,"uid":178651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"譚副校有冇轉校？"},{"pid":"a09053e93265e473fa6b285593906e62613f075e","tid":1711400,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f8620dc315b0e3a988f1fdccc0563ef0cd27cd","tid":1711400,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"052fbd66735f6ba7adb24c29f95bf203a0e32473","tid":1711400,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:28:13.000Z","msg":"見到隔離有個post話 德望學校扮中立打壓學生<br />\n其實高主教書院亦面對同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校指希望冷處理 但實際上打壓學生自由 討好建制陣營的校友<br />\n<br />\n校友陣容鼎盛如下：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張建宗<br />\n曾偉雄<br />\n鄭承隆<br />\n鄭耀棠<br />\n石禮謙<br />\n<br />\n舊生會更加由成日話要打曱甴比人起埋底嘅快＿美太子爺把持<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆被迫改名為意見牆</span></span></strong><br />\n校方指連儂牆帶有政治意味以及較近示威者的立場，因此理應保持中立，易名為意見牆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5／11早會默站行動及Lunchtime操場靜坐</span></span></strong><br />\n早前有校內學生被補，校內關注組發起早會默站行動以聲援被捕同學。<br />\n校方以活動期參加者有機會提及被捕同學，對其保釋有所影響而禁止。<br />\n校方